{{Lunisolar November}} '''November 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[990]] {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – An era change was made from {{ill|Eizoku (Japan)|ja|永祚 (日本)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} via {{ill|era change|ja|改元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Kenmu|ja|建武|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year / {{ill|Engen|ja|Engen|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1336]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} consulted with the brothers {{ill|Zeien|ja|是円|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Masae|ja|真恵|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , and established the {{ill|Kenmu Shikimoku|ja|建武式目|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . The {{ill|Muromachi Shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was founded. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1634]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – An Iga vendetta incident occurred: Watanabe Kazuma dueled with Kawai Matagorō and others in a {{ill|duel|ja|決闘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , with Araki Mataueimon assisting (in what became known as the {{ill|Kagiya no Tsuji Duel|ja|鍵屋の辻の決闘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1853]] {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} appointed Nakahama Manjirō ({{ill|John Manjiro|ja|ジョン万次郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) to a construction role. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1854]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} occurred.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1579]] {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Hidemoto|ja|毛利秀元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of the {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1650]] ).
