1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1853]] {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} appointed Nakahama Manjirō ({{ill|John Manjiro|ja|ジョン万次郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) to a construction role. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1854]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} occurred.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1579]] {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Hidemoto|ja|毛利秀元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of the {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1650]] ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 60th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[130]] {{ill|December 24|ja|12月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 12th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and father of {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1195]] ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1628]] {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ono Tadaaki|ja|小野忠明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a swordsman and instructor to the shogunal family.
