== Events == * {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[990]] {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日}} ) – An era change was made from {{ill|Eizoku (Japan)|ja|永祚 (日本)}} to {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦}} via {{ill|era change|ja|改元}} . * {{ill|Kenmu|ja|建武}} 3rd year / {{ill|Engen|ja|Engen}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1336]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji}} consulted with the brothers {{ill|Zeien|ja|是円}} and {{ill|Masae|ja|真恵}} , and established the {{ill|Kenmu Shikimoku|ja|建武式目}} . The {{ill|Muromachi Shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate}} was founded. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1634]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日}} ) – An Iga vendetta incident occurred: Watanabe Kazuma dueled with Kawai Matagorō and others in a {{ill|duel|ja|決闘}} , with Araki Mataueimon assisting (in what became known as the {{ill|Kagiya no Tsuji Duel|ja|鍵屋の辻の決闘}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1853]] {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日}} ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate}} appointed Nakahama Manjirō ({{ill|John Manjiro|ja|ジョン万次郎}} ) to a construction role. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1854]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日}} ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake}} occurred.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1579]] {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Hidemoto|ja|毛利秀元}} , lord of the {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩}} (died [[1650]] ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇}} 60th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[130]] {{ill|December 24|ja|12月24日}} ) – {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇}} , the 12th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇}} and father of {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル}} (born [[1195]] ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1628]] {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日}} ) – {{ill|Ono Tadaaki|ja|小野忠明}} , a swordsman and instructor to the shogunal family.
