{{Lunisolar November}} 
'''November 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)}}  the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦}}  1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}}  [[990]]  {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日}} ) – An era change was made from {{ill|Eizoku (Japan)|ja|永祚 (日本)}}  to {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦}}  via {{ill|era change|ja|改元}} .
* {{ill|Kenmu|ja|建武}}  3rd year / {{ill|Engen|ja|Engen}}  1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}}  [[1336]]  {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji}}  consulted with the brothers {{ill|Zeien|ja|是円}}  and {{ill|Masae|ja|真恵}} , and established the {{ill|Kenmu Shikimoku|ja|建武式目}} . The {{ill|Muromachi Shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate}}  was founded.
