* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永}}  7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  [[1854]]  {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日}} ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake}}  occurred.

