{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月初七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 7일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[990]] {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=}} ) – An era change was made from {{ill|Eizoku (Japan)|ja|永祚 (日本)|qq=}} to {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=}} via {{ill|era change|ja|改元|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kenmu|ja|建武|qq=}} 3rd year / {{ill|Engen|ja|Engen|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1336]] {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=}} consulted with the brothers {{ill|Zeien|ja|是円|qq=}} and {{ill|Masae|ja|真恵|qq=}} , and established the {{ill|Kenmu Shikimoku|ja|建武式目|qq=}} . The {{ill|Muromachi Shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate|qq=}} was founded. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1634]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|qq=}} ) – An Iga vendetta incident occurred: Watanabe Kazuma dueled with Kawai Matagorō and others in a {{ill|duel|ja|決闘|qq=}} , with Araki Mataueimon assisting (in what became known as the {{ill|Kagiya no Tsuji Duel|ja|鍵屋の辻の決闘|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1853]] {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}} appointed Nakahama Manjirō ({{ill|John Manjiro|ja|ジョン万次郎|qq=}} ) to a construction role. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1854]] {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake|qq=}} occurred.
== Births == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1579]] {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Hidemoto|ja|毛利秀元|qq=}} , lord of the {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|qq=}} (died [[1650]] ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|qq=}} 60th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[130]] {{ill|December 24|ja|12月24日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|qq=}} , the 12th {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=}} and father of {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=}} (born [[1195]] ). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1628]] {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ono Tadaaki|ja|小野忠明|qq=}} , a swordsman and instructor to the shogunal family.
