* {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=}}  1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}}  [[990]]  {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=}} ) – An era change was made from {{ill|Eizoku (Japan)|ja|永祚 (日本)|qq=}}  to {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=}}  via {{ill|era change|ja|改元|qq=}} .
