* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=}}  11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}}  [[1634]]  {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|qq=}} ) – An Iga vendetta incident occurred: Watanabe Kazuma dueled with Kawai Matagorō and others in a {{ill|duel|ja|決闘|qq=}} , with Araki Mataueimon assisting (in what became known as the {{ill|Kagiya no Tsuji Duel|ja|鍵屋の辻の決闘|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=}}  6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}}  [[1853]]  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}}  appointed Nakahama Manjirō ({{ill|John Manjiro|ja|ジョン万次郎|qq=}} ) to a construction role.
