'''November 7''' is the 7th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}  the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=|12=draft}}  1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  [[990]]  {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – An era change was made from {{ill|Eizoku (Japan)|ja|永祚 (日本)|qq=|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Shōryaku|ja|正暦|qq=|12=draft}}  via {{ill|era change|ja|改元|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Kenmu|ja|建武|qq=|12=draft}}  3rd year / {{ill|Engen|ja|Engen|qq=|12=draft}}  1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  [[1336]]  {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|12=draft}}  consulted with the brothers {{ill|Zeien|ja|是円|qq=|12=draft}}  and {{ill|Masae|ja|真恵|qq=|12=draft}} , and established the {{ill|Kenmu Shikimoku|ja|建武式目|qq=|12=draft}} . The {{ill|Muromachi Shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate|qq=|12=draft}}  was founded.
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}}  11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  [[1634]]  {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – An Iga vendetta incident occurred: Watanabe Kazuma dueled with Kawai Matagorō and others in a {{ill|duel|ja|決闘|qq=|12=draft}} , with Araki Mataueimon assisting (in what became known as the {{ill|Kagiya no Tsuji Duel|ja|鍵屋の辻の決闘|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft}}  6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  [[1853]]  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|12=draft}}  appointed Nakahama Manjirō ({{ill|John Manjiro|ja|ジョン万次郎|qq=|12=draft}} ) to a construction role.
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft}}  7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  [[1854]]  {{ill|December 26|ja|12月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake|qq=|12=draft}}  occurred.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}}  7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  [[1579]]  {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mōri Hidemoto|ja|毛利秀元|qq=|12=draft}} , lord of the {{ill|Chōfu Domain|ja|長府藩|qq=|12=draft}}  (died [[1650]] ).

== Deaths ==
