* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}}  5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  [[1628]]  {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ono Tadaaki|ja|小野忠明|qq=|12=draft}} , a swordsman and instructor to the shogunal family.

