== Events == * [[:en:Shōryaku|Shōryaku]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:990|990]] [[:en:November 26|November 26]] ) – An era change was made from [[:en:Eiso (era)|Eizoku (Japan)]] to [[:en:Shōryaku|Shōryaku]] via {{ill|era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/era change|qq=|1=era change|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11498853}} . * [[:en:Jianwu|Kenmu]] 3rd year / {{ill|Engen|ja|Engen|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Engen|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1336|1336]] [[:en:December 10|December 10]] ) – {{ill|Ashikaga Takauji|ja|Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Takauji|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} consulted with the brothers {{ill|Zeien|ja|是円|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zeien|qq=|1=Zeien|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q84977487}} and {{ill|Masae|ja|真恵|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Masae|qq=|1=Masae|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q85271929}} , and established the {{ill|Kenmu Shikimoku|ja|建武式目|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenmu Shikimoku|qq=|1=Kenmu Shikimoku|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q4226141}} . The {{ill|Muromachi Shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Muromachi Shogunate|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} was founded. * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1634|1634]] [[:en:December 26|December 26]] ) – An Iga vendetta incident occurred: Watanabe Kazuma dueled with Kawai Matagorō and others in a [[:en:Duel|duel]] , with Araki Mataueimon assisting (in what became known as the [[:en:Igagoe vendetta|Kagiya no Tsuji Duel]] ). * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 6th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1853|1853]] [[:en:December 7|December 7]] ) – The {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|1=Tokugawa shogunate|2=ja|3=江戸幕府|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo Shogunate|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} appointed Nakahama Manjirō ([[:en:Nakahama Manjirō|John Manjiro]] ) to a construction role. * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 7th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1854|1854]] [[:en:December 26|December 26]] ) – The {{ill|Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|ja|豊予海峡Earthquake|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyoyo Strait Earthquake|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} occurred.
== Births == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 7th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1579|1579]] [[:en:November 25|November 25]] ) – [[:en:Mōri Hidemoto|Mōri Hidemoto]] , lord of the [[:en:Chōfu Domain|Chōfu Domain]] (died [[:en:1650|1650]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Keikō Tennō]] 60th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:130|130]] [[:en:December 24|December 24]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Keikō Tennō]] , the 12th [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor]] and father of {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q461258}} (born [[:en:1195|1195]] ). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 5th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1628|1628]] [[:en:December 2|December 2]] ) – [[:en:Mikogami Tenzen|Ono Tadaaki]] , a swordsman and instructor to the shogunal family.
